@page "/"
<PageTitle>Home</PageTitle>

<div class="docs-page">
    <h1>Welcome to DrawnUI for Blazor</h1>
    <p class="docs-lead">This sandbox collects focused DrawnUI samples for controls, graphics, gestures, advanced rendering, and gaming scenarios running in WebAssembly.</p>
    <p class="docs-note">Use the left navigation to open sections as you need them. The default route now starts on this lightweight home page instead of jumping straight into a heavy demo.</p>

    <div class="docs-example-frame" style="padding: 24px; margin-top: 16px;">
        <h2 style="margin-top: 0;">Start Here</h2>
        <p>Browse the sandbox by intent:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Presentation</strong> for the landing page and richer showcase samples.</li>
            <li><strong>Tutorials</strong> for guided examples like cards.</li>
            <li><strong>Controls</strong>, <strong>Graphics</strong>, and <strong>Effects</strong> for targeted component probes.</li>
            <li><strong>Gaming</strong> for heavier accelerated scenes like Space Shooter and Parallax.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>The Space Shooter demo is still available from the <strong>Gaming</strong> section.</p>
    </div>
</div>